I am yet to come to terms with this loss, it feels extremely personal and I can’t wrap my head around the gravity of it still. I cant help but continuously think of how i used to sit for hours watching every possible video centered around them on the internet, scream to their songs, cry watching their documentary and dream of one day seeing and meeting them as a 12 year old. And now that I’ve been rewatching those as a 20 year old, with Payno gone, my heart is shattering. One Direction hasn’t been just a boy band or just music to me, it’s something that saved me which is why i am so deeply affected by it all. 

Liam, i am sure you’re in a better place (with no spoons to scare you) and i hope you know how loved you were and how much love we’ll always hold for you. 
My heart goes out to his family, the boys, and especially Bear.
Love forever 🤍 #liam #liampayne #onedirection #onedirectionedits
